analysis_metadata.methodology: Monte Carlo + Strategic Alternatives + Integration Planning

key_risks: Medical Director departure would impact physician relationships
Operations Manager critical for service delivery
Lead Aesthetician has significant customer following
recommendations: Immediate retention agreements for Medical Director and Operations Manager
Cross-training program to reduce key person dependency
Performance incentive structure tied to practice growth

key_activities: Review all vendor and supplier contracts
Assess IT systems and patient records
Begin staff training and development programs
success_metrics: Marketing spend normalized to 14% of revenue

key_activities: Launch expanded wellness and weight loss services
Plan location expansion or service additions

risk_mitigation: Contingency planning for key personnel departure

optimal_strategy.rationale: Highest expected value considering probability and transaction costs

recommendations: Build relationships with strategic healthcare buyers early
Maintain financial reporting suitable for institutional buyers
Document operational processes for smooth due diligence
Develop management team capable of operating independently

investment_conditions: Quarterly performance reviews with defined milestones
